on demand behind one OpenAI-compatible API; you pay per token.

Don't have a key yet?
  1. Sign in or create an account:  {KEY_CONSOLE_URL}
  2. Open: API Keys
  3. Create a key and copy it (it is shown only once).

Paste your key below — input is hidden, and nothing is stored until it verifies."""


